    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, either as a major restoration project or for parts. The engine currently does not turn over, and there are visible signs of significant rust on the frame and lower body panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are non-functional. It will require a trailer for transport, as it is not currently road-worthy, but it remains a complete donor car for someone looking for specific original components.",
